        <abstract> 
<p>CD’s pessimistic view [of prospective sale of <hi rend="italic">Insectivorous plants</hi>] is to blame for the small printing. Murray’s printed only 1250 copies and sold 1700. A thousand more have been ordered.</p> 
        </abstract>
